casebody.data:
TRAYFORD
v.
NC PSYCHOLOGY BOARD. No. 649A05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 24, 2006. Sondra C. Panico, Assistant Attorney General, for N.C. Psychology Board. J. Heydt Philbeck, Raleigh, for David K. Trayford, M.S.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 23rd day of January 2006 by Plaintiff for extension of time to file brief:

"Motion Allowed. Plaintiff (David K. Trayford, M.D.) shall have up to and including the 13th day of February 2006 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court. By order of the Court in conference this the 24th day of January 2006."
